Class CheckPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.transit.airport.security.CheckPoint

  • public class CheckPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Checkpoint represents a security checkpoint line and its line, where the front Passenger is undergoing the actual security process.

    zcollins
